					<p style="direction: rtl;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/WeeklyRanger-e1274592896628.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-102" title="WeeklyRanger" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/WeeklyRanger-e1274592896628.png" alt="" width="373" height="100" /></a></p>
